title: You'll Feel Like You're on Vacation at our Resort Style Pool and Spa!
posting_body: ['Your adventure starts here-welcome to The Markham apartments in Cupertino.', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x283', 'From $4,349', '.', '2 Bed 2 Bath .', '1045 Sq.Ft', 'Markham Apartments', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Address:', '20800 Homestead Road Cupertino, CA 95014', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Visit The Markham Apartments and find out what this two-bedroom, two-bathroom residence has in store for you!', 'This home provides a stainless steel appliance package for convenience in meal preparation.', 'Individuals can easily clean spills and stains from granite countertops.', 'The in-house washer and dryer eliminate the need to wash clothes elsewhere.', 'With ample space in each closet, individuals gain storage options for personal belongings.', 'This apartment even comes with a deck, perfect for relaxation or recreation.', "By becoming a neighbor of this pet-friendly neighborhood, you'll have exclusive access to the topnotch amenities such as a saltwater pool, a hydrotherapy spa, and a twenty-four-hour fitness center.", 'Everyone can look forward to a variety of activities at the clubhouse and the business center.', 'The Markham offers an on-site electric vehicle charging station, as well as additional storage.', 'For current terms, pricing, and availability, call or email now.', 'FLOORPLAN SPECIALS', '2 Weeks Free on Select Apartments', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x283', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'DISCLAIMER:', 'Call for details: pricing/availability subject to change at any time.']
